{"tid":492544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【首次勝訴】LEGO發火控2公司侵權 包裝標誌似成咁","createTime":"2017-12-07T15:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T16:04:09.000Z","uid":161311,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"be1c54bb4a1beaf5478ec6aecfb2fa3102d6b092","tid":492544,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:40:49.000Z","msg":"路透社報道，歐洲最大玩具製造商樂高（LEGO）在中國贏得版權訴訟！樂高今發佈聲明表示，廣東省汕頭市中級人民法院已判決，兩間內地玩具公司製造的博樂（BELA）產品侵犯了樂高的版權，並且在製造與銷售過程出現不公平競爭行為。<br />\n<br />\n這是樂高首次在中國版權官司中勝訴，據報，汕[i頭市中級人民法院今年9月已作出裁決，但直至11月才開始生效。樂高勝訴後，該兩間內地公司不可再模仿樂高的包裝和標誌製作或銷售產品。<br />\n<br />\n以博樂BELA作為品牌的玩具由兩家中國企業製造與販售，和樂高旗下LEGO系列幾乎完全相同。樂高勝訴後，這兩家企業不可再仿照樂高的包裝和商標製造產品。<br />\n<br />\n今年較早時北京市高級人民法院認定，樂高的標誌與名稱在中國為「知名」商標，使樂高在商標侵權訴訟中佔有優勢。"},{"pid":"ef35e47fd00a8c603938094eac77af0d91f41128","tid":492544,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:44:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/234407_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F234407_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6b82a51d&s={SIZE}\" /> 薄樂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/234411_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F234411_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d75948f6&s={SIZE}\" /> lego"},{"pid":"50b539a19750ff0b38b0cf89d82d4fb60ca6b134","tid":492544,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:46:47.000Z","msg":"係都告Lepin 先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db39162547f2c4d0b1adc646cbae36797efd1057","tid":492544,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime